snippet.title: Exil Kickstarter Teaser (2024)
snippet.description:
Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mys/exilgame
Exil is coming to Kickstarter September, 2024!
A Mystical Anime-Inspired Metroidvania. Embark on an adventure through a mystical world full of magical creatures.
